{"word":"G927 - βαρύτιμος - barýtimos - bar-oo'-tim-os - Very precious","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βαρύτιμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">barýtimos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">bar-oo'-tim-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Very precious</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"விலையேறப்பெற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"of weighty (great) value, very precious, costly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G926 - βαρύς - barýs - bar-ooce'/926\">G926</a> and <a href=\"#/G5092 - τιμή - timḗ - tee-may'/5092\">G5092</a>; highly <i>valuable:</i> - very precious.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}